tyle=\"color: red;\">Hong Kong was ceded to Britain after the Opium War.</span></em>"},{"pid":"11fb851df4dfa3bcea87f1aebe8507e0efec6d15","tid":635253,"uid":45232,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"7be6fc008161a27301a32f86bc5a88ccfe4a2779","tid":635253,"uid":13257,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d165ddd2d84661d7434b99c865242db33e3fda1b","tid":635253,"uid":77196,"like":96,"dislike":0,"score":96,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T03:58:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>至於「中國堅持收回香港主權」，楊潤雄回應時稱中國一直擁有香港主權，故不涉及收回或不收回。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n割撚咗都仲擁有？你賣撚咗間屋過十年同個屋主講你一直擁有間屋嘅主權得唔得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:01:45.000Z","msg":"佢似覺得係間屋我一直都擁有，你只係幫我管理間屋。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:09:29.000Z","msg":"大陸一直宣稱自己有香港主權(即使係97前)<br />\n所以香港唔係殖民地<br />\n同時無左殖民地既權利<br />\n包括但不限於獨立公投<br />\n<br />\n遲啲你話&ldquo;香港曾經係英國既殖民地&rdquo;<br />\n港共都會話你錯<br />\n因為共產黨話唔係<br />\n港府過多幾年就會改埋<br />\n但全世界既人都知事實係點"},{"pid":"def186b1c152dcf440259d9952d34e13050d89b8","tid":635253,"uid":14918,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:10:06.000Z","msg":"淘寶免運費先"},{"pid":"fba5560dca36edc15d9389f2b11ae4693ed7ab29","tid":635253,"uid":158158,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:10:35.000Z","msg":"淘寶都當我地係境外人"},{"pid":"350b6cce131084f49d44d3b15498bf7a0d48c257","tid":635253,"uid":15777,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"8c032d8b93292718e2175dc167b19ccec795495f","tid":635253,"uid":77196,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T03:59:55.000Z","msg":"他指「香港位於中國南方」的語句可以有不同解釋，包括香港<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>位於中國境外的南方或位於中國境內的南方</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢d雞毛蒜皮嘅野係得d弱智先會咁留意 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:13:41.000Z","msg":"中國南方可以解中國以外嘅南方 即係越南泰國嗰堆<br />\n但係位於中國境內的南方就只可以解中國境内<br />\n講到尾都係統戰 <br />\n可能班弱智以為因為啲咁簡單嘅嘢就導致港獨思潮嘅出現"},{"pid":"00513fb6a9e6bb0f545756d33e02c4eb68cd8c31","tid":635253,"uid":36901,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:14:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://big5.locpg.hk/gate/big5/www.qstheory.cn/books/2016-08/31/c_1119485398_4.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbig5.locpg.hk%2Fgate%2Fbig5%2Fwww.qstheory.cn%2Fbooks%2F2016-08%2F31%2Fc_1119485398_4.htm&d=jxAsTADpIS2eYGc%2BVBnRACwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=3af031ff\" target=\"_blank\">http://big5.locpg.hk/gate/big5/www.qstheory.cn/books/2016-08/31/c_1119485398_4.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n局長9up前唔該睇下鄧小平文選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n在時機已經成熟了，應該明確肯定：一九九七年中國將收回香港。就是説，中國要<span style=\"color: red;\">收回</span>的不僅是新界，而且包括香港島、九龍〔11〕。中國和英國就是在這個前提下來進行談判，商討解決香港問題的方式和辦法。如果中國在一九九七年，也就是中華人民共和國成立四十八年後還不把香港<span style=\"color: red;\">收回</span>，任何一個中國領導人和政府都不能向中國人民交代，甚至也不能向世界人民交代。如果不<span style=\"color: red;\">收回</span>，就意味著中國政府是晚清政府，中國領導人是李鴻章〔12〕！"},{"pid":"b60f0dbef6f255766adca6baf1d03ee6b42070f1","tid":635253,"uid":48083,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:15:01.000Z","msg":"中華人民共和國政府和大不列顛及北愛爾蘭聯合王國政府滿意地回顧了近年來兩國政府和兩國人民之間的友好關係，一致認為通過協商妥善地解決歷史上遺留下來的香港問題，有助於維持香港的繁榮與穩定，並有助於兩國關係在新的基礎上進一步鞏固和發展，為此，經過兩國政府代表團的會談，同意聲明如下：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>一、中華人民共和國政府聲明：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">收回</span>香港地區（包括香港島、九龍和&ldquo;新界&rdquo;，以下稱香港）是全中國人民的共同願望，中華人民共和國政府決定於１９９７年７月１日對香港<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>恢復</ins>行使主權</span>。</strong></span><br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cmab.gov.hk/tc/issues/jd2.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cmab.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fissues%2Fjd2.htm&d=jxAsTADpIS2eYGc%2BVBnRACwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=008ac0fd\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cmab.gov.hk/tc/issues/jd2.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n冇失去過權又洗咩恢復??<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">結論:<br />\n同中国人講信用講合約精神<br />\n係哂鳩氣</span></span></strong></strong></span></div>"},{"pid":"559726d75a9ab4762aba24eee2daa32be9d0723b","tid":635253,"uid":60287,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:15:04.000Z","msg":"切勿將教材政治化"},{"pid":"20b010362d7fc702824eebf346ab9a2e8a4505a4","tid":635253,"uid":77196,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"00513fb6a9e6bb0f545756d33e02c4eb68cd8c31","tid":635253,"uid":36901,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:14:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://big5.locpg.hk/gate/big5/www.qstheory.cn/books/2016-08/31/c_1119485398_4.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbig5.locpg.hk%2Fgate%2Fbig5%2Fwww.qstheory.cn%2Fbooks%2F2016-08%2F31%2Fc_1119485398_4.htm&d=jxAsTADpIS2eYGc%2BVBnRACwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=3af031ff\" target=\"_blank\">http://big5.locpg.hk/gate/big5/www.qstheory.cn/books/2016-08/31/c_1119485398_4.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n局長9up前唔該睇下鄧小平文選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n在時機已經成熟了，應該明確肯定：一九九七年中國將收回香港。就是説，中國要<span style=\"color: red;\">收回</span>的不僅是新界，而且包括香港島、九龍〔11〕。中國和英國就是在這個前提下來進行談判，商討解決香港問題的方式和辦法。如果中國在一九九七年，也就是中華人民共和國成立四十八年後還不把香港<span style=\"color: red;\">收回</span>，任何一個中國領導人和政府都不能向中國人民交代，甚至也不能向世界人民交代。如果不<span style=\"color: red;\">收回</span>，就意味著中國政府是晚清政府，中國領導人是李鴻章〔12〕！"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:15:45.000Z","msg":"死咗n年，唔洗聽佢支笛 (好似係"},{"pid":"d1d95fea5fbf8fb7fb0af7e6283b98e8a0a11f7f","tid":635253,"uid":27909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:16:40.000Z","msg":"On9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"425854967df1235d20a18d4740048a2a3fb8f840","tid":635253,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"